{
  "uid": "v12-0-drilldown",
  "title": "Grafana 12.0 \u2014 Drilldown Suite",
  "description": "Showcases the Drilldown suite that went GA in 12.0 (Metrics / Logs / Traces / Profiles) plus live signals from each datasource so you can see why you would drill down.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "v12.0",
    "drilldown",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-15m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_prom",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prom"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "ds_loki",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "loki",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Loki",
          "value": "loki"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "ds_tempo",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "tempo",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Tempo",
          "value": "tempo"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "ds_pyro",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "grafana-pyroscope-datasource",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Pyroscope",
          "value": "pyroscope"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10000,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "tags": [
        "demo-guide"
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1.2rem;background:#1a2a3a;border-left:4px solid #5794f2;border-radius:6px;font-family:system-ui\"><div style=\"font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8aa9d0;margin-bottom:.3rem\">DEMO GUIDE</div><div style=\"font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Grafana 12.0 \u2014 Drilldown Suite</div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem\"><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#5794f2;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83c\udfaf What you're looking at</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Drilldown is the GA-in-12.0 way to explore metrics, logs, traces and profiles. It replaces the old Explore view with purpose-built apps per signal type.</div></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#73bf69;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83e\uddea Try this</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Click any of the app links at the top \u2014 Metrics / Logs / Traces / Profiles. You don't have to write a query; pick a service and the app does the rest.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:.8rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:1px solid #2d3e54;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udcda <strong style=\"color:#fff\">Learn more</strong>: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana-cloud/visualizations/simplified-exploration/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Grafana docs</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/whatsnew/whats-new-in-v12-0/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">v12 What's New</a></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Open a drilldown app\n\n[\u27a1 Metrics Drilldown](/a/grafana-metricsdrilldown-app) \u00b7 [\u27a1 Logs Drilldown](/a/grafana-lokiexplore-app) \u00b7 [\u27a1 Traces Drilldown](/a/grafana-exploretraces-app) \u00b7 [\u27a1 Profiles Drilldown](/a/grafana-pyroscope-app)\n\nThe four panels below surface live signal **from the data source each drilldown sits on top of** \u2014 click any panel title \u2192 *View* to jump into Explore, or use the links above to enter the drilldown UI directly."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Metrics \u2014 HTTP request rate (Prometheus)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (status_code) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "HTTP {{status_code}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "calcs": [
            "mean"
          ]
        }
      },
      "description": "Metrics \u2014 HTTP request rate (Prometheus). Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana-cloud/visualizations/simplified-exploration/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Logs \u2014 Grafana container (Loki)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_loki}",
        "type": "loki"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "{container=\"grafana12_grafana\"}",
          "maxLines": 200
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "dedupStrategy": "none"
      },
      "description": "Logs \u2014 Grafana container (Loki). Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana-cloud/visualizations/simplified-exploration/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Traces backend health (Tempo)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 21
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "up{job=\"tempo\"}",
          "legendFormat": "tempo up"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "DOWN",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "UP",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Traces backend health (Tempo). Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana-cloud/visualizations/simplified-exploration/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Profiles backend health (Pyroscope)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 21
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "up{job=\"pyroscope\"}",
          "legendFormat": "pyroscope up"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "DOWN",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "UP",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Profiles backend health (Pyroscope). Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana-cloud/visualizations/simplified-exploration/"
    }
  ]
}